==================
Description:
==================
It's a very simple, cozy home, with a nice view of Whiterun.
Your companion will follow you inside.

This mod is cleaned with TES5Edit

(I do not understand English very well, sorry!



***

This mod is a remake of the "Onboro House".
There is no compatibility.
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/64790/?



==================
Location:
==================
It's nestled snugly on a hill behind the farms of Whiterun.

Key is in Porch Chest.


==================
Requirements:
==================
All you need is the latest version of Skyrim.
and Hearthfire.(Texture is required)



==================
Craft equipment
==================
Oven
Cooking Pot
Enchanting Table
Alchemy Lab
Tanning Rack
Workbench
Grindstone
